---
title: Chicken Sausage & Spinach-Ricotta Ravioli with Grape Tomatoes & Lemon
description: Mamma mia! Here’s some perfect pasta prepared at pronto speed. The sauce starts with tomato and chicken sausage that cook up quickly in the pan. Once you’ve got your water boiling, in go the ravioli, which become al dente in a flash since they’re fresh. After that, all you gotta do is finish the creamy sauce and it’s buon appetito!

***The image pictured is similar to our Chicken Sausage & Spinach-Ricotta Ravioli—but not exact! As always, please consult the ingredients list for more detailed recipe information and allergens.***
